    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of Toona native to eastern and southeastern Asia. Used as an ornamental, as a food, and for its hard and reddish timber in furniture making.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
